## For AI Agents

When working autonomously:
1. Check DOCUMENTATION_INDEX.md first
2. Never create files in root (except listed above)
3. Always update READMEs when adding files
4. Follow decision tree for placement
5. Update master index for architecture docs
6. Preserve organization - don't move files without reason

## Enforcement

These rules are MANDATORY. Pull requests that violate these rules will be rejected.

If unsure about placement:
1. Check similar existing files
2. Review directory README.md
3. Follow decision tree
4. Ask before creating in root
